 Galvatron landed at a near by valley. It would give him room to try out this 
new body. His robot mode was unfinished. On his way here he picked up a 
signal from one with a powerful spark signature. It was Magnus. He would 
regonize him anywhere. He would deal with them later.
 Apocalypse landed close behind as did death. They looked over the bot. His 
robot mode was pure silverish color. Very smooth. He had a silver tail with a 
sharp pointed cone at the end of it.His dragon ribs where exposed across his 
stomach. His chest had a green gem in the center of it. His red dragon head 
layed agaisnt his back. His silver wings where not expanded and grew more 
tense. There where no visible weapons on him. But he doubted that that was 
the case. or maybe he had yet to get all the DNA he needed.....
